name: Instant Download-Retro Recipe Cards Folded 2
description:
Retro Personalized Recipe Folded Card 2
When you need a little more space for a longer recipe
(instant digital download / does not include printed item)

............❝{INCLUDES}❞..............................................................................
• 8" x 6" ( 4' x6" when folded) flat templates.....1 on a page
• Optional Back Print

Options: You can choose to print these with the design on back ( also included) or blank. You also have the option of filling in your name and recipe name before printing or you can print blank (If you choose not to the form fields will not be visible in printing. :)


............❝{MATERIALS NEEDED}❞..............................................................
• Color Printer ( home or other)
• 8.5" x11" Letter size cardstock ( 80lb-110lb weight)
• Cutting blade ( like X-acto Knife) or Paper Cutter (can purchase at craft store)
• Straight Edge ( like ruler / prefer wooden with no slip back) or T-Square
• Adobe Reader ( can download for free at http://get.adobe.com/reader)


............❝{ORDERING}❞..............................................................................
• This is an "INSTANT DOWNLOAD" , which means you will receive your item as soon as your purchase is complete


............❝{PRINTING}❞................................................................................
• You may print your design at home , copy shop ( Kinkos, Staples, etc) , with an online printer or with a professional printer.

• This printable uses a printing format that all professional use, but some printers may have
additional and/or specific criteria. If you are using a professional printer , please ask them what
are their document requirements. We also suggest printing a sheet of your printable and take a
copy to them to review.

• Please note that if you are using an online printer ( like Catprints, UPrints, 123Prints, 48hourprints or etc) then the printing format is different. If you advise which online printer you are using, we will send you your file in the correct format at no additional cost. Please contact us prior to purchase if this option is needed.

• If you are printing at home, also of local copy/print shops offer professional cutting for a very low fee. Just always give them a few more sheets, just in case.

• We can print your purchase on a variety of cardstock finishes for you for an additional fee. Please contact use for prices and options.

............❝{COLORS}❞.................................................................................
• Colors appear different on different monitors and especially once they are printed out. Your monitor shows colors in RGB & your printer prints CYMK.

• We suggest you print out a copy of our color chart above or you may provide us with a Hex Code or Pantone (PMS) Uncoated Code. If you do not see a color close to what you need , we do have a Pantone Uncoated Color Chart that we can send you. This chart includes over 700 colors , so if you are trying to match a specific color, this will give you a better change.


............❝{PAPER}❞.....................................................................................
• Our templates were designed for 80lb-100lb weight cover stock. You can use standard paper weight when applicable, but we suggest printing a sample out prior.

• There are several place to purchase card stock
1. Paper-Source.com ( has a variety of store locations around USA as well)
2. LCIpaper.com
3.Papersandmore.com
4. Your local craft store or office supply store ( like Michael's, Office Max, Staples and etc)

• Please note that standard office supply card stock is normally 65lbs and has a very matte finish. This doesn't mean that you cannot use it, but it may feel a little lighter in weight that what you see/feel in stores. We suggest a minimum of 80lbs (which majority of home printers can take comfortably) and a maximum of 110lb ( highest recommended for standard home printers,but some may easily go thru the printer). If you have any doubts, buy a few sheets of different weight and print you template. If it doesn't thru easily without and stoppage, then your paper weight is good. If it stutters or jams, then the weight it so heavy for printer. DO NOT FORCE THE PAPER THRU YOUR PRINTER AS IT MIGHT DAMAGE IT.


............❝{MATCHING ITEMS}❞...................................................................
• Matching items are available upon request. Please contact us if you would like a matching item (applicable fees apply)


............❝{ADDITIONAL INFO}❞...................................................................
• All files and templates are copyright of Gramkin Paper Studio and are for personal use only.

name: Spell It Out
description:
Are you sick of wasting valuable minutes of your life that you can't get back by turning down the overly confident pursuer?

Then try a courtesy card! These handy little cards are the perfect size to get the job done!

When you don't want to be bothered and can't waste anytime, simply reach for a card and hand it over to the offender... 
and walk away....just let the card do the rest

This set includes 10 flat 2" x 3.5" cards printed on our lux textured cardstock with the following saying"

"Apparently I have to spell it out for you......N.O"

What a small price to pay for peace of mind! 
and remember when you can't say it to someones face...... 
Say it in a card!
